<% if(!currentUser) { %>
  <div class="row">
  	<div class="col l8 offset-l2 center">
  		<h3 class="flow-text">The place to find friends to build & code your next project with!</h3>
  		<p class="justify">There is a huge community of hobbyists building projects with single board computers and a variety of software. Maker Collab brings
  		this community closer, to enable collaboration on projects without the need to join an expensive ‘maker-space’.
